{"tid":509261,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人發覺自己開始唔多飲到甜野......","createTime":"2017-12-25T06:30:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T14:38:01.000Z","uid":75100,"like":1258,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":124,"replies":[{"pid":"36b5853dc4b62992f87f80f25f7d7dbbedf5b4e5","tid":509261,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T06:30:51.000Z","msg":"有陣見維他檸檬茶特價，口渴買枝諗住試下，點知超甜又澀喉，飲完好似喉嚨仲唔舒服左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n岩岩朋友買完一排益力多送左枝比我，我見好耐無飲過咪要左，點知甜到飲唔到落口，逼自己先飲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n明明得20幾歲, 但已經覺得茶先係世界第一，係咪好老積<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明以前飲阿華田仲可以加2匙糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e376fb4f57b9ce1dbd7a4e96ad2a5b0e892c4a","tid":509261,"uid":38876,"like":273,"dislike":3,"score":270,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T06:32:44.000Z","msg":"益力多一飲會起晒痰"},{"pid":"ae2ed7e7f7e34b6ebda8330bf24e468a963d710a","tid":509261,"uid":65256,"like":35,"dislike":4,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T06:39:09.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_b.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_g.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_p.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/shocking_y.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 飲一啖都覺得甜到瀨屎<br />\n但平時食甜野又甜到漏到OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4311c83b0361dd7ded27eee4c48300fb0b3c8b9f","tid":509261,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45e376fb4f57b9ce1dbd7a4e96ad2a5b0e892c4a","tid":509261,"uid":38876,"like":273,"dislike":3,"score":270,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T06:32:44.000Z","msg":"益力多一飲會起晒痰"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T06:39:31.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以D人話咩益力多、乳酪對腸胃好，我都無福消受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da11535da15e78ad3cc7569c18f286315c6bca43","tid":509261,"uid":69013,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T06:40:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>益力多一飲會起晒痰</blockquote>我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以D人話咩益力多、乳酪對腸胃好，我都無福消受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原味乳酷唔甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5496a315b0db4abde1c4857bd41b844e036b509d","tid":509261,"uid":152123,"like":4,"dislike":73,"score":-69,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T06:41:31.000Z","msg":"自細都係咁 依家二十歲已經唔識嚟月經<br />\n樓主下世小心啲"},{"pid":"04e186829b453b4486bba46f7ddfa292601549f4","tid":509261,"uid":147789,"like":86,"dislike":3,"score":83,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T06:42:13.000Z","msg":"係維他啲果汁同檸檬茶都好撚甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講起又係而家去茶記飲熱飲都好少落糖<br />\n出街口痕最多會買茶飲<br />\n人大咗好似變到鍾意清啖野"},{"pid":"44840308527bb7aebad315a7715350b0ce2af397","tid":509261,"uid":11148,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T06:43:41.000Z","msg":"一樣,基本上只飲荼同咖啡<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eceaaee29730dd5d5dd793d33908717c81e560b","tid":509261,"uid":2377,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T06:54:55.000Z","msg":"食太甜會甜到喉嚨那住痛"},{"pid":"b014902f1f2fab306f7d0d288fed51cbdbd2adef","tid":509261,"uid":152047,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T07:11:40.000Z","msg":"唔係好事咩<br />\n事實上係啲嘢飲真係太甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5ba957e0181892ca8430fbec16f619558bf8d39","tid":509261,"uid":143468,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T07:14:12.000Z","msg":"由細到大都唔飲甜嘢"},{"pid":"872ea8c5ddb2078bdaf56e37b65913a470e20103","tid":509261,"uid":75100,"like":1,"dislike":2,"