:2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b014902f1f2fab306f7d0d288fed51cbdbd2adef","tid":509261,"uid":152047,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T07:11:40.000Z","msg":"唔係好事咩<br />\n事實上係啲嘢飲真係太甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T07:14:38.000Z","msg":"當味覺變到太敏感，你就發現好多野都食唔到飲唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T07:43:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大把人廿幾歲仲狂灌汽水可樂. 依家意識到仲好, 身體冇咁多毛病"},{"pid":"236450b03a11623aa5368ffcaf56008335a875d9","tid":509261,"uid":92278,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T07:50:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自細都係咁 依家二十歲已經唔識嚟月經<br />\n樓主下世小心啲</blockquote><br />\n麻甩佬黎咩月經"},{"pid":"ec47d90ba6f51298c978b25ec0a2bbf502dcbb8c","tid":509261,"uid":19556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1d64c0dfd7002e50b2bedb3c8ec395fc0a2c11e","tid":509261,"uid":73093,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T07:31:49.000Z","msg":"反而我已經唔會飲汽水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T07:51:28.000Z","msg":"5 6年冇飲過<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5b370d2ac0eb14a6c8fe808be2d3538f9675e6e","tid":509261,"uid":7458,"like":5,"dislike":14,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T07:51:43.000Z","msg":"我都係咁<br />\n細個成日好想飲汽水<br />\n但係屋企人係過節先準飲<br />\n大個左人地請我都唔飲<br />\n多糖既零食都係一舊起兩塊止<br />\n自己煮野唔會落太多糖 最多10g<br />\n去餐廳飲咩都要走甜 <br />\n食到太甜既野會覺得好嘔心 直頭想反胃<br />\n而家計住自己唔好一日食多過50g糖<br />\n好似今日聖誕係屋企整火雞咁 一粒糖都冇落過<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb24d419e61b102f9c39e0706021d9187c6c1342","tid":509261,"uid":46151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T07:54:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>酸辣苦都有層次。 甜係死甜爛甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n甜都有唔同種類"},{"pid":"d485dcd1d07a4747a84f981709e2267e3eb6c23c"