62992f87f80f25f7d7dbbedf5b4e5","tid":509261,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T06:30:51.000Z","msg":"有陣見維他檸檬茶特價，口渴買枝諗住試下，點知超甜又澀喉，飲完好似喉嚨仲唔舒服左<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n岩岩朋友買完一排益力多送左枝比我，我見好耐無飲過咪要左，點知甜到飲唔到落口，逼自己先飲到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n明明得20幾歲, 但已經覺得茶先係世界第一，係咪好老積<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明以前飲阿華田仲可以加2匙糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T09:27:55.000Z","msg":"但你有無覺身體好左先 始終啲罐裝 包裝飲品咁多糖 少飲/唔飲其實係好事"},{"pid":"8a87cc67036c1a48f3bd679001b7873f1d0dd1b8","tid":509261,"uid":19858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T09:37:25.000Z","msg":"有人送左盒大維他檸茶俾我<br />\n一直無勇氣開<br />\n應該飲兩啖會唔想飲"},{"pid":"d6a2a2b2568d620eb6e7373ccd4d3e69a04dc6a5","tid":509261,"uid":144529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T09:39:14.000Z","msg":"我20歲已經好少飲甜野同汽水 特別係汽水已經好耐無飲 依咖都係飲水，茶較多<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69b3b42947bef8b3bdbfde8e4b9e8bab03c22cbb","tid":509261,"uid":34256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T09:40:41.000Z","msg":"以前唔鐘意飲茶 覺得唔夠甜冇味<br />\n而家開始飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07818bfcad32117c0f6ae38c3eee88cafb5dc409","tid":509261,"uid":154644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T09:42:00.000Z","msg":"我已經好耐無飲甜野!<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb095beccbb994daefa6406564759470953e619b","tid":509261,"uid":56467,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T09:51:32.000Z","msg":"飲唔到甜野都可以叫春..."},{"pid":"291d78895229fe5f51311fd47ff5c015f12e2be9","tid":509261,"uid":1485,"like":0,"dislike":25,"score":-25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T10:05:06.000Z","msg":"近期超鍾意飲呢支<img src=\"/assets/f